title: Flight Simulator 2020 - POI's - USA - Our Lady of the Rockies
description:
In this video we will fly over Our Lady of the Rockies. Our Lady of the Rockies is a 90-foot (27 m) statue built in the likeness of Mary, the mother of Jesus, that sits atop the Continental Divide overlooking Butte, Montana.
